    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BIG LOOT</strong> - 一款关于商队、贸易与生存的Roguelike冒险。探索世界，明智选择装备与路线——前往下个城镇的道路充满惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级马车</strong>：用收集的资源打造零件。添加箱子携带更多战利品，或加固车轮确保送达。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/6028493342b5e24fff1594c917f78807.poster.avif?t=1772204142\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/6028493342b5e24fff1594c917f78807.webm?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/6028493342b5e24fff1594c917f78807.mp4?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每次旅程都不同</strong>：离镇时选择路线——安全（但收益低）或危险（但战利品丰厚）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/e441ea7f325cf2c94643ace65cb54854.poster.avif?t=1772204142\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/e441ea7f325cf2c94643ace65cb54854.webm?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/e441ea7f325cf2c94643ace65cb54854.mp4?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>口袋不伸缩，但背包会！</strong> 它真的会因战利品变鼓。战斗前最好放下…但小心别让货物滚走！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/8086594a86e436caccc288fcec2fecfc.poster.avif?t=1772204142\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/8086594a86e436caccc288fcec2fecfc.webm?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/8086594a86e436caccc288fcec2fecfc.mp4?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战利品与交易</strong>：寻找贵重物品，与游商贸易，提升关系来获取稀有商品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/83d917d1709853f9eb6e23b10bbbf864.poster.avif?t=1772204142\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/83d917d1709853f9eb6e23b10bbbf864.webm?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116730/extras/83d917d1709853f9eb6e23b10bbbf864.mp4?t=1772204142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
